CONTROLLED VS UNCONTROllED IN Forms
//CONTROLLED.....
1.Value of the input field updated in real-time
2.Component access the value as it being typed
//UNCONTROllED.......
1.Not updated in realtime
2.Component can access the value the form is submitted. 
//Use Ref()......
To access a Input field value.
//Event.Prevent Default().......
Used to Prevent the Page from Refreshing When the form is Submitted.
//event.target.value......
Component access the value as it being typed
